{"tid":443974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(反黑)點解反黑組好似好大權力？","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T16:01:29.000Z","uid":83913,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a71f8e2434adae6956331d447b2b23fe4f0dee96","tid":443974,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁"},{"pid":"070cb7fd80fe9f65a092e6eab5404eea761d0a96","tid":443974,"uid":57410,"like":15,"dislike":56,"score":-41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"相傳意大利籍神父利瑪竇明末來華傳教<br />\n早期多活躍於澳門及廣州一帶 <br />\n由於意大利粉一般不附湯 <br />\n利瑪竇神父對華南麵食文化不太接受 <br />\n於是每次出外用餐，點選湯麵時多會要求店家將麵和湯分開送上 <br />\n乾麵上桌後再混以肉碎、蠔油或豉油加以調製作肉醬意粉狀，是為對家鄉菜的思念 <br />\n利瑪竇的食法後來被廣傳開去，民間爭相仿傚，稱為&quot;鬼佬麵&quot;，亦即粵人第一代&quot;鬼佬西餐&quot;<br />\n由於忌諱，粵人後來把鬼字刪除成為今日兩廣一帶稱呼的&quot;撈麵&quot; <br />\n店家雖多不理解利瑪竇不喝湯的背後原意，但一般仍然會奉送清湯，以示本店乃正宗利瑪竇食法 <br />\n清湯伴撈麵另上成為明末廣州高格調食店的象徵 <br />\n後因滿清乾隆修定&quot;四庫全書&quot;，&quot;清湯&quot;一詞有眨滿清之意而故事被刪去 <br />\n致有關記載盡失，只剩小部份老廣州以口耳相傳方式流傳典故 <br />\n<br />\n但撈麵造法流傳至今"},{"pid":"0abbbc7dc6b382a94756b8169c708f57d595c7e9","tid":443974,"uid":5713,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"反黑套野好多都亂嚟 唔洗太認真"},{"pid":"0eaf5af47389b037c0e01c73059b2cf9d5fb2205","tid":443974,"uid":14440,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到"},{"pid":"d28ebc7b9ae99d927154ac23dcefc52306f93643","tid":443974,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但便裝一柴可以點軍裝三柴做野？"},{"pid":"f5a715b4fac4b2fef4d5d782f3784a102feedc3a","tid":443974,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但便裝一柴可以點軍裝三柴做野？</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔得 但都可以俾下建議咁<br />\n總之現場一定係便裝話事"},{"pid":"3abb4486bfd6f53692a5100e363a84bf8bf17b3d","tid":443974,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但便裝一柴可以點軍裝三柴做野？</blockquote><br />\n約定俗成架啫 你當便裝高半級咁囉"},{"pid":"1c877c7c806212a9587d0f2e8b38bab5fe74c91d","tid":443974,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但便裝一柴可以點軍裝三柴做野？</blockquote><br />\n約定俗成架啫 你當便裝高半級咁囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係三柴就老撚都唔聽一柴反黑枝笛"},{"pid":"9928d6800abcaa5a8ac5ff1b5c1400e1e19a3745","tid":443974,"uid":83913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"同埋點解反黑呢套野，B1組得五個人？"},{"pid":"bc503304ee6b20e5af858d9323c5b21822703006","tid":443974,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"軍裝白衫都俾個反黑 pc 點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f83724366ce2cc44c45054ef1a6b41a3c3c9c5f","tid":443974,"uid":24513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"反黑咪即係黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b3bb9a963a48fc6f0db4c0e91f7a771185597d","tid":443974,"uid":88194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個反黑組係咪得6個人<br />\n6個就應付到全港既黑社會<br />\n真係個個骨格精奇 聰明絕頂 人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87be78a2173d84e4c662e17a70cbd47677ad9592","tid":443974,"uid":14651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個反黑組係咪得6個人<br />\n6個就應付到全港既黑社會<br />\n真係個個骨格精奇 聰明絕頂 人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9d57650c44fb9e8c32307c06e167d6d4f08a96","tid":443974,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"鳳凰哥叫到唔係唔去呀嘛"},{"pid":"0f8d45c7be231a15038406e2c2e2e36c0e0bcaec","tid":443974,"uid":4412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"床哥~~"},{"pid":"1a748d1c9348fbcf8020443cf8fb256921f1e00c","tid":443974,"uid":51269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個反黑組係咪得6個人<br />\n6個就應付到全港既黑社會<br />\n真係個個骨格精奇 聰明絕頂 人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反黑套戲，陳小春係<br />\n個b1係一個組。而佢地係負責一個環頭單一嘅字頭<br />\n<br />\n而唔係負責哂成個全港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6336b1bc7dcacda67003f672db6d8f3822cdb1","tid":443974,"uid":51269,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主，唔好以為軍裝好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，軍裝係差佬入面最低層但又最多人。以前有人講過差佬做多幾年，多數會將佢地分入組 例如cid 反黑etc<br />\n<br />\n如果你都係軍裝的話 一係能力有問題 一係冇上進心，得罪人<br />\n<br />\n咁樣計法軍裝咁廢，反黑梗係騎住佢地<br />\n<br />\n同埋軍裝入面個堆多數都好熄事寧人出糧度日，日案件發生就會幾廿架車咁出去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，（視情乎反黑cid會唔會出動），所以唔係好似電影入面咁，任達華警長咁撚串搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2689985a34c2a3f57eb3d6f1bdd12da2fabc38","tid":443974,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n邊個話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我識有人當左一年兵就轉左做雜差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d88d79114909735073e0593a69cce569bbb544d","tid":443974,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T20:01:28.000Z","msg":"最記得秦沛嗰句，原來係黑腳，奴才之中既奴才"},{"pid":"ff37a9a25bc701423d6accc12fdc3f92d19e282e","tid":443974,"uid":35285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T20:18:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7ee7b123126e97c53f90fdfb6d38afa32ef6fc5","tid":443974,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T20:53:16.000Z","msg":"又反又黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4466fc1a53b70dcb6a76460b9e8388a328cba4","tid":443974,"uid":18100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解可以隨時調動 ptu?<br />\n<br />\n 同埋d 軍裝好似當正佢哋上司咁</blockquote><br />\n便裝係現場不嬲都可以點軍裝做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為便裝要撈好多年先入到</blockquote><br />\n便裝都可以係pc仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ff3608e62480ee822422806263bc4c81fbf419","tid":443974,"uid":26385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最記得秦沛嗰句，原來係黑腳，奴才之中既奴才</blockquote><br />\n而加都係樂土，不過係我雷洛嘅國土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c52d8a1e913ee7fee7a2b9f08a81548bee4cd2","tid":443974,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"雜項調查小隊又高軍裝半級？"},{"pid":"986b9eb68df1a2686c849762dafdf6bdbf9af2c6","tid":443974,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"首先調部門要過3年試用期，冇話咩便裝要好耐先轉到"}]}